			<div class="content" id="post-content-2343186">
									

<p>This is, hopefully, the first step in a grand scheme to compile, revise, and expand all of my relevant pieces into a single canon. Of course, I am moving somewhat backwards in this, as the last tale I posted back in March, <a href="/when-we-came-home">When We Came Home</a>, was the end of the story. Now we get the beginning.</p>
<p>Stay tuned, there is more to come.</p>
<p>e: The brothers death are of course from Dmatix's <a href="/scp-1440">SCP-1440</a>. The woman at the end I will not name at the moment, but the clever reader (or one I already told) might be able to identify her.</p>
<p>ee: This was a particularly fun piece to write, in no small part because of the fun of seeing everything fall into place when I weave it together. We've got the openings of Genesis and John, a little bit of Dark Souls, even a little Malazan in here.</p>

